Package: rtemis
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Advanced Machine Learning and Visualization
Date: 2026-02-01
Authors@R: person(given = "E.D.", family = "Gennatas", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), 
    email = "gennatas@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9280-3609"))
Description: A comprehensive machine learning and visualization package with an 
    'S7' backend featuring rigorous type checking and value validation, paired with an 
    efficient, user-friendly functional API. A single call to 'train()' can handle preprocessing, 
    training, hyperparameter tuning, and testing - streamlining workflows with unparalleled 
    efficiency. Supports supervised learning with automatic nested resampling, probability 
    calibration, unsupervised learning (clustering, decomposition). The user maintains
    complete control over all configuration options and hyperparameters through 
    transparent, type-checked and validated 'setup_*()' functions. Supports data.frames, 
    data.tables, and tibbles, parallel execution, and interactive visualizations.
